若S為一個三個面的骰子,
P(面一)=1/5,
P(面二)=2/5,
P(面三)=2/5




H
(
X
)
=


1
5



log

2


⁡
(
5
)
+


2
5



log

2


⁡

(


5
2


)

+


2
5



log

2


⁡

(


5
2


)



{\displaystyle H(X)={\frac {1}{5}}\log _{2}(5)+{\frac {2}{5}}\log _{2}\left({\frac {5}{2}}\right)+{\frac {2}{5}}\log _{2}\left({\frac {5}{2}}\right)}


聯合熵(Joint Entropy)與條件熵(Conditional Entropy)[編輯]
聯合熵由熵的定義出發，由聯合分佈，我們有:





H
(
X
,
Y
)
=

∑

x
∈


X





∑

y
∈


Y






p
(
