)



)


{\displaystyle H(X,Y)=\sum _{x\in {\mathcal {X}}}\sum _{y\in {\mathcal {Y}}}^{}p(x,y)\log({\frac {1}{p(x,y)}})}



條件熵，顧名思義，從條件機率p(y|x)做定義:





H
(
